                     <interp inst="def1-1027-18490409" type="surname" value="SEXTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1027-18490409" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">HENRY SEXTON,</hi>
                  </persName>
                  <rs id="t18490409-1027-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18490409-1027-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="breakingPeace"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18490409-1027-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="wounding"></interp> feloniously stabbing <persName id="t18490409-name-1111" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1111" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1111" type="surname" value="MCCARTHY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1111" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18490409-1027-offence-1 t18490409-name-1111"></join>John McCarthy</persName>, with intent to do him some grievous bodily harm.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. W. J. PAYNE</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">conducted the Prosecution.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1112" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1112" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1112" type="surname" value="MCCARTHY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1112" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN MCCARTHY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a labourer of Stratford. On Sunday, 4th March, I met the prisoner, who I had worked with, and said, "Henry, you want shaving;" he said, "Yes, I do, <hi rend="italic">Jack—I</hi> said, "Let me shave you," and <hi rend="italic">shoved</hi> this broom across his face—he made a kick at me—I rubbed it across his face again; he. said "You b----b----, I will rip your b----guts open"—he put his basket down and pulled a knife out—I ran across the road, and did not know he was behind me till I felt him stab me—I said, "I am stabbed" he said, "Go along"—I put my hand behind me, and showed it him full of blood—I became senseless—Perry took me to a doctor.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1113" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1113" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1113" type="surname" value="PERRY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1113" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PERRY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a boilermaker, and was with M'Carthy—I saw him brush the prisoner's face several times—the prisoner made a kick at him, and threw the basket from his shoulder; took a knife out, ran after him, and stabbed him, then picked up the basket and walked away—I heard him say, "You b----b----, I will rip your guts open if you do that again!"—I said,</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184904090186"></xptr>
               <p>"Harry, you have stabbed the man;" he said, "I know I have, and a b----good job too"—the broom did not strike him, it only brushed him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did not I give you half my tobacco? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes. <hi rend="smallCaps">SAMUEL WATFORD</hi>. I am an engineer—I saw M'Carthy brush the prisoner's face—the prisoner made a kick at him, and M'Carthy brushed him across the face again—the prisoner dropped his basket, took a knife out, opened it, put it by his side, and placed his right hand over the blade; M'Carthy brushed him across the face again and ran away; the prisoner ran after him and stabbed him—I said, "What a villain you must be to stab a man in the back like that;" he said, "He should have let me alone"—I asked a gentleman to hold him, and took the knife from his pocket—there was blood on the blade.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1114" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1114" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1114" type="surname" value="TUCKET"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1114" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH TUCKET</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman</hi>). I found M'Carthy bleeding dreadfully from a wound in the side; I produce his trowsers, here is a cut in them corres<lb></lb>ponding with the wound—the prisoner said, "He should not have hit me with the broom."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1115" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1115" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1115" type="surname" value="HOLMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1115" type="given" value="WILLIAM HENRY"></interp>WILLIAM HENRY HOLMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a surgeon at the London Hospital—the prosecutor was brought there on 4th March with a wound in the small of the back, an inch wide and an inch and a half deep; it had bled a great deal, it was not dangerous, but it would have been if it had been a little more on one side.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I have had my head cut open, and often do not know what I am doing; my head has been sown up; I have a scar two inches long. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> There are marks on his forehead and the top of his head—they are old wounds.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1116" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1116" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1116" type="surname" value="COX"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1116" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM COX</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Thamespoliceman</hi>). I have known the prisoner sixteen or eighteen years—he was always quiet and inoffensive—they play all manner of games with him, and push him down—his brother is an idiot.</p>
               <p>
